<a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/celebrity/priyamani">Priyamani</a> as Rahim&#39;s wife Runa lends solid support. She is full of heart.<br />
<a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/celebrity/gajraj-rao">Gajraj Rao</a> as the controversial sports journalist Prabhu Ghosh, and Rudranil Ghosh who essays the role of the President of the Indian Football Federation, honestly play their parts but are let down by some clich&eacute;d writing.<br />
Rishab Joshi as Rahim&#39;s son Hakim is wonderful.<br />
