Siddhant Chaturvedi as Imaad is terrific. He gets into the skin of the character and delivers a knockout performance that really required him to be his most vulnerable self.<br />
Ananya Panday as Ahana is impressive. She delivers a mature performance and is extremely real and honest in her act. Also, she has a great eye for complex human dramas like Gehraiyaan and now Kho Gaye Hum Kahan<br />
