Sanjana Sanghi as AK&#39;s daughter Sakshi does justice to her strong author-backed role. She brings the right amount of vulnerability and anger in her performance.<br />
Every other supporting actor in the film like Parvathy Thiruvothu as the nurse Ms Kanan, Jaya Ahsan as Naina, Dilip Shankar as Tyagi, Paresh Pahuja as Arjun among others, only compliments the film.</p>

<h2 id="66bf0e6a52fa1"><strong>Final Verdict:</strong></h2>

<p>Kadak Singh is an interesting and an intriguing film that could have been more impactful had the middle portions not been sluggish. Regardless, its novel concept is a reason enough to watch it.<br />
