<p>In the past, we have watched movies like Luca and Soul. Such hard-hitting films that stay&nbsp;with you for a long time. Elemental, on the other hand, fails a bit short of originality. There are multiple themes that Disney has tried to cover but at some point, you might feel that this isn&#39;t a rom-com.&nbsp;</p>

<h2><strong>Star Performance</strong></h2>

<p><a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/hollywood/elemental-ending-explained-what-happened-to-wade-and-ember-at-the-end-find-out-1226164">Wade </a>played by&nbsp;Mamoudou Athie stole the show with his very lovable character. On the other hand, Ember played by Leah Lewis perfectly portrays a character with anger issues who just wants to pursue her dream.</p>

