Karan Tacker plays his part fine as the IPS officer Amit Lodha, who later gets promoted to the SP&#39;s (Superintendent of police) position. <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/tv/news-gossip/ravi-kishan-adds-bhojpuri-tadka-drama-companys-sets-386268">Ravi Kishan</a> (Abhyuday Singh) as the manipulative don is convincing. Avinash Tiwary as Chandan Mahto will make you forget that he was the same man in the Bollywood film, Laila Majnu. Ashutosh Rana, as usual, has made his character his second skin. Nikita Dutta as Amit Lodha&#39;s wife justifies her role.&nbsp;</p>

